Shared / Cross-Role Features

Global search bar in header: searches courses, users (role-scoped), announcements, resources
Profile page for all users: edit name, avatar (upload), change password, notification preferences
Responsive design: fully usable on tablet (768px+); mobile layout acceptable but desktop-first
Skeleton loaders on every data-fetching screen — never show blank white space while loading
Empty states on every list/table: descriptive message + primary action button (e.g., "No courses yet. Create your first course.")
Confirmation dialogs for all destructive actions: delete, suspend, remove
Form validation: client-side with inline errors, server-side errors surfaced in a toast
Pagination on all tables: 20 rows per page default, configurable to 50/100
URL-driven state: filters, pagination, and active tab reflected in URL query params so pages are shareable and back-button safe


API Design

RESTful API with consistent response envelope:
json{ "success": true, "data": {}, "meta": { "page": 1, "total": 240 }, "error": null }
All list endpoints support: ?page=, ?limit=, ?sort=, ?order=asc|desc, ?search=, plus entity-specific filters. Full OpenAPI/Swagger docs auto-generated and accessible at /docs.

Error Handling & Edge Cases

401 → redirect to login, preserve intended URL for post-login redirect
403 → show "Access Denied" page with back button
404 → custom page with navigation options
500 → generic error page with a request ID for support
Network failure → show inline retry button, never a blank screen
File upload failure → surface the exact error (file too large, wrong type, quota exceeded)
Session expiry → silent token refresh; if refresh fails, redirect to login with "Session expired" message